It’s official the Brow Frame Pencil and Brow Blowout Gel is available right now!! 🥳😆🫶 Thank you all for the love on our New brow pencil shape!

 I was honestly nervous to release it because it’s not a shape everyone is used to seeing from a brow pencil, but I was determined to create micro-bladed hair without using a brow pen. 

I tested countless brow pens and decided I wanted something with effortless instant results without having to work for it. A product that works for you!

Everyone’s response made me so happy I took the risk to create this unique shape 🥹🫢and I hope you all love it, The excitement is REAL! 🦋 have been floating in my stomach all week!!! I hope you all love them🫶
